name: Experiment Or Die #73
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Another movie from when we were kids that should have been scary was Dawn of The Dead. A bunch of people hole up in a mall in the Zombie apocalypse and try and survive. I remember sleeping over at my friends house and watching this and HillS Have Eyes and just not being spooked at all. Actually the hill people were creepier than the incredibly slow zombies. I guess reality is worse than our imagination. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
